## Modules
- Single Responsibility Principle per module.
- Use snake_case for file names.
- Document all public APIs with examples (`///`).
- Group by function (e.g., `auth`, `cache`, `nim`).

## Structure
- Separate API handlers from core logic (service layer).
- Define clear interfaces using traits for testability.
- Enforce visibility rules (pub/private).
- Prevent circular module dependencies.